{"type":"message","id":"75ed96e1","parentId":"b260df4a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:13:31.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture of the current state:\n\n1. **CFI research is progressing** - they've done experiments showing CFI-weighted compression beats frequency-only on precision, but loses recall catastrophically\n2. **The key insight**: constant-format tokens (freq=160, CFI=1.0) are metaprogramming artifacts that look causal but aren't\n3. **Next experiment pending**: Hybrid CFI×Freq^0.5 scoring (Strategy C)\n4. **The bigger picture**: Compositional Cognition with three layers - Compression (Layer 1), Causal (Layer 2), Compositional (Layer 3)\n\nLet me now do the arxiv scan (Part 2), then work on advancing the research.\n\n\nI'm checking what's already been documented about arxiv relevance to avoid duplicating work, then I'll search for relevant papers and push forward with the next experiment—either implementing Strategy C or refining the CFI scoring approach—before committing everything.","thinkingSignature":"6c02674d05948c1d19401c5f7bda755b10cf957fd8c9f16834047f5fd5107ec9"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me do the arxiv scan and then advance the research.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s4ngjlba4ugx_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"sparse autoencoder causal features LLM reasoning 2025 2026","count":5,"freshness":"year"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s4ngjlba4ugx_2","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"causal discovery causal inference mixture experts 2025","count":5,"freshness":"year"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12793,"output":322,"cacheRead":12050,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25165,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774376002794}}
